        &lt;h1&gt;Getting Started with BigLedger&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your essential first steps with BigLedger&amp;rsquo;s Business Operating System. This section covers everything you need to know to get up and running quickly and efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Quick Start Guide&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;quick-start-guide&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#quick-start-guide&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;New to BigLedger? Follow this path for the fastest onboarding experience:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-cards hx:mt-4 hx:gap-4 hx:grid not-prose&#34; style=&#34;--hextra-cards-grid-cols: 3;&#34;&gt;
