    &lt;a href=&#34;#next-steps&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Once you complete the Getting Started section:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/user-guide/basic-operations/&#34; &gt;Basic Operations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Learn fundamental daily tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/user-guide/daily-tasks/&#34; &gt;Daily Tasks&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Master routine business operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/user-guide/administration/&#34; &gt;Administration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Configure advanced system settings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/user-guide/best-practices/&#34; &gt;Best Practices&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Optimize your BigLedger usage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Need Help?&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;need-help&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#need-help&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;📧 Email Support&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:sales@bigledger.com&#34; &gt;sales@bigledger.com&lt;/a&gt; for general questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;💬 Technical Support&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:vincent@bigledger.com&#34; &gt;vincent@bigledger.com&lt;/a&gt; for technical assistance&lt;/li&gt;
